des: Progressive Senator Victoria Steele (D, AZ) and DC-based liberal journalist Jimmy Zuma provide a summary and analysis of political events and interview newsmakers and influencers. Whether you want to be the best-informed player on social media, at the dinner table, or around the water cooler, Wait, What? is your source for ideas, facts and talking points.
